configuration.packets

Enum SPInstr

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<SPInstr>
      • configuration.packets.SPInstr
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<SPInstr>

    public enum SPInstr
extends java.lang.Enum<SPInstr>
    SPInstr for Server Packet Instructions
    Defines the byte codes structuring a packet from client to server or server to client
    Packet configuration : ([KEY BYTE] CONTENT [EOM]){0,2} [ACTION BYTE] [EOP]
    Key bytes are :
    • BOM
    • USER
    • PASS
    • CMD

    Action bytes :
    • WAIT_CMD
    • WAIT_AUTH
    • CLOSE
    Author:
    Romain Mormont
